---
title: Chicken and Ramen Noodle Stir Fry with Thai Sweet Chili Sauce
description: This sumptuous stir fry is a veritable greatest hits of delicious flavours and fresh crispy veggies. We’re so excited to bring you Thai sweet chili – the perfect balance of spicy and tasty. We also guarantee that this meal will come together faster than take-out!
